      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Apply relevant biotransformation rules that match the observed mass difference between the anchor and suspect to generate candidate structures\u2014derivatives\u2014for the query spectrum",
      "asbval:note": "Confirmed as a prerequisite condition in the paper's methodology.",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10-1021-acs-analchem-4c01565",
