    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/reference-prediction-comparison-evaluation/000",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "BAM successfully generated the correct suspect structure in 4171 cases, achieving a recall of 24.2% when a derivative is generated... BAM demonstrated impressive accuracy in ranking the correct derivatives, achieving an average rank of 2.1 and ranking the correct suspect first in 57.7% of cases",
      "asbval:note": "The paper explicitly evaluates BAM predictions against reference annotations (known structures from the global molecular network) and reports recall, ranking accuracy, and coverage metrics.",
