      "asbval:target_claim_field": "research_question",
      "asbval:target_claim_text": "Compare pipeline predictions against reference annotations to compute validation metrics (accuracy, coverage) for molecular structure discovery. This skill quantifies how well a method reproduces known molecular structures in a benchmark dataset.",
